{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e9db5e9284","title":"给马××的一封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3ac8157ecd","index":0,"year":1951,"month":11,"day":15,"articleId":"e9db5e9284","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8177661581","type":"title","text":"给马××的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e9db5e9284","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92a486f249","type":"paragraph","text":"××","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e9db5e9284","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e03ec8972","type":"paragraph","text":"关于学生健康问题前与先生谈过。此问题深值注意，提议采取行政步骤，具体地解决此问题，提出健康第一，学习第二的方针。我认为（中共华东局一月十一日电报一件付上，请察阅，其中第三项谈此词题，）是正确的，请马付部长同志商酌处理为朌。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e9db5e9284","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff344cbdc8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e9db5e9284","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a1d02ac013","type":"subdate","text":"一九五一年十一月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e9db5e9284","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"609c84340d","type":"paragraph","text":"附：中共华东局一月十一日电报","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e9db5e9284","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e9fa6806f3","type":"paragraph","text":"“健康第一，学习第二”","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e9db5e9284","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa43888426","type":"paragraph","text":"——节录中共华东局一月十一日向中央报告关于学校工作的指示电文","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e9db5e9284","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"333635c900","type":"paragraph","text":"“......","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e9db5e9284","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ecd99a19e","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）转入正常学习，又须防止过去加多课程硬赶功课的偏向。此次参加军校学生之体格检查中，即可看出，由于国民党长期反动统治的结果，学生体质虚弱，患病者很多。但解放以来，各地也未能很好注意‘健康第一，学习第二’之原则，因此造成公立学校之体格最差，大学较中学又差的现象还严重存在，这点应引起十分警惕。应按华东局高教会议的规定，适当减少正课时间，照顾学生健康需要。......”","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e9db5e9284","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"72e1b3e38f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席批语：这是正确的。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"e9db5e9284","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":48,"end":47}}}},"__N_SSG":true}